high_descs: Move forward, then face right to the island with the bread and knife.
Pick up the knife from the island.
Turn left, then right around the island and face left towards the sink.
Cut the green apple in the sink.
Turn right, then right again around the island and face left towards the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge and close it.
Turn left, then left again around the island and face right towards the sink.
Take the apple slice from the sink.
Turn right, then right again and face left towards the fridge.
Put the apple slice in the fridge, close it, and take it out again.
Turn left, then left again around the island and move towards the microwave on the counter.
Put the apple slice in the microwave and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold apple slice in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk straight, towards the sink, until you reach the oven, then turn right so that you are facing the kitchen island.
Pick up the knife, in front of the bread, closest to the edge of the island.
Turn to your left and walk straight until you reach the kitchen counter, then turn right and walk to the kitchen sink.
Cut the apple in the back of the sink in half.
Turn right and walk to the end of the counter, turn right again and stop in front of the refrigerator.
Place the knife in the refrigerator on the shelf next to the red pepper.
Turn left and walk to the corner of the counter, then left again and walk to the sink, stopping in front of it.
Pick up a piece of the apple in the back of the sink that was previously cut.
Turn right and walk to the end of the counter, then right again to go back to the refrigerator.
Place the apple slice in the refrigerator, to the left of the knife, shut the refrigerator door, wait a moment, then remove the apple from the refrigerator.
Turn left and walk to the corner of the counter, then left again and walk to the microwave.
Place the apple in the microwave and shut the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean, chilled, apple slice into the microwave.

high_descs: go forward slightly, then turn right to face the knife in front of the loaf of bread and grey cup
take the knife from the counter
turn left and cross the room to the sink
cut the apple in the sink
cross the room to the refrigerator
place the knife on the top shelf of the refrigerator, to the left of the tomato, and close the door
turn left and return to the kitchen sink
take an apple wedge from the sink
return to the refrigerator
place the apple wedge to the left of the knife in the refrigerator and close the door, wait 8 seconds, and remove the apple wedge, closing the door afterward.
turn around and cross the room to the microwave
place the apple wedge in the front right corner of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a slightly cooled apple wedge in the microwave while abandoning the knife in the refrigerator

high_descs: Walk forward and turn right to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Turn left and walk forward to face the sink.
Cut the apple in the sink into 3 pieces.
Turn right and walk forward to face the fridge.
Place the knife on the top shelf of the fridge.
Turn left and walk forward to face the sink.
Pick up a piece of apple from the sink.
Turn right and walk forward to face the fridge.
Cool the apple in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Place the piece of apple inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cut plus cool a piece of apple as well as place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk halfway across the room and turn right to face the table with a knife on the edge.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the table.
Walk around the room to face the sink.
Cut the apple into 3 pieces.
Walk around the room to the right and turn left to face the fridge.
Put the knife in the fridge on the shelf with the tomato.
Walk around the room to the left and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up a piece of the apple in the sink.
Walk around the room to the right and turn left to face the fridge.
Cool the piece of apple in the fridge.
Walk around the room to the left and face the microwave.
Place the apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cut an apple, cool it, and store in the microwave.
